INTALL
======

1.) Unzip.

2.) Upload.

3.) Run the SQL files "tables.sql" and "default_data.sql" in /database

4.) Set /public_html/config/config.php and /public_html/config/database.php

5.) Permissions.
	
	cd /home/pyrocms/
	chmod 777 codeigniter/cache
	chmod 777 codeigniter/logs
	chmod -R 777 public_html/temp
	chmod -R 777 public_html/uploads
	chmod -R 777 public_html/assets/img/galleries
	chmod -R 777 public_html/assets/img/products
	chmod -R 777 public_html/assets/img/staff
	chmod -R 777 public_html/assets/img/suppliers

6.) Go to your web root, login as "demo@example.com" with the password "password" and make yourself an admin user account.

7.) Log into your new account and delete demo@example.com.